"Enter a valid вҖңslugвҖқ consisting of Unicode letters, numbers, underscores, or "
"hyphens."
msgstr ""
"Indtast en gyldig вҖңslugвҖқ bestГҘende af Unicode-bogstaver, cifre, understreger "
"eller bindestreger."

#, python-format
