msgid "CSRF verification failed. Request aborted."
msgstr "CSRF-verifikationen mislykkedes. ForespГёrgslen blev afbrudt."

msgid ""
"You are seeing this message because this HTTPS site requires a вҖңReferer "
"headerвҖқ to be sent by your web browser, but none was sent. This header is "
"required for security reasons, to ensure that your browser is not being "
"hijacked by third parties."
msgstr ""
"Du ser denne besked fordi denne HTTPS-webside krГҰver at din browser sender "
"en вҖңReferer headerвҖқ, som ikke blev sendt. Denne header er pГҘkrГҰvet af "
"sikkerhedsmГҰssige grunde for at sikre at din browser ikke bliver kapret af "
"tredjepart."

msgid ""
"If you have configured your browser to disable вҖңRefererвҖқ headers, please re-"
"enable them, at least for this site, or for HTTPS connections, or for вҖңsame-"
"originвҖқ requests."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du har opsat din browser til ikke at sende вҖңRefererвҖқ headere, beder vi "
"dig slГҘ dem til igen, i hvert fald for denne webside, eller for HTTPS-"
"forbindelser, eller for вҖңsame-originвҖқ-forespГёrgsler."

msgid ""
"If you are using the <meta name=\"referrer\" content=\"no-referrer\"> tag or "
"including the вҖңReferrer-Policy: no-referrerвҖқ header, please remove them. The "
"CSRF protection requires the вҖңRefererвҖқ header to do strict referer checking. "
"If youвҖҷre concerned about privacy, use alternatives like <a "
"rel=\"noreferrer\" вҖҰ> for links to third-party sites."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du bruger tagget <meta name=\"referrer\" content=\"no-referrer\"> eller "
"inkluderer headeren вҖңReferrer-Policy: no-referrerвҖқ, sГҘ fjern dem venligst. "
"CSRF-beskyttelsen afhГҰnger af at вҖңRefererвҖқ-headeren udfГёrer stringent "
"referer-kontrol. Hvis du er bekymret om privatliv, sГҘ brug alternativer sГҘ "
"som <a rel=\"noreferrer\" вҖҰ> for links til tredjepartswebsider."

msgid ""
"You are seeing this message because this site requires a CSRF cookie when "
"submitting forms. This cookie is required for security reasons, to ensure "
"that your browser is not being hijacked by third parties."
msgstr ""
"Du ser denne besked fordi denne webside krГҰver en CSRF-cookie, nГҘr du sender "
"formularer. Denne cookie er pГҘkrГҰvet af sikkerhedsmГҰssige grunde for at "
"sikre at din browser ikke bliver kapret af tredjepart."

msgid ""
"If you have configured your browser to disable cookies, please re-enable "
"them, at least for this site, or for вҖңsame-originвҖқ requests."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du har slГҘet cookies fra i din browser, beder vi dig slГҘ dem til igen, "
"i hvert fald for denne webside, eller for вҖңsame-originвҖқ-forespГёrgsler."

